{"tha-ap148:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap148:0.2":"Chattavagga ","tha-ap148:0.3":"6 Anulepadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap148:1.1":"“Anomadassimunino, ","tha-ap148:1.2":"bodhivedimakasaham; ","tha-ap148:1.3":"Sudhaya pindam datvana, ","tha-ap148:1.4":"panikammam akasaham. ","tha-ap148:2.1":"Disva tam sukatam kammam, ","tha-ap148:2.2":"anomadassi naruttamo; ","tha-ap148:2.3":"Bhikkhusanghe thito sattha, ","tha-ap148:2.4":"imam gatham abhasatha. ","tha-ap148:3.1":"‘Imina sudhakammena, ","tha-ap148:3.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap148:3.3":"Sampattim anubhotvana, ","tha-ap148:3.4":"dukkhassantam karissati’. ","tha-ap148:4.1":"Pasannamukhavannomhi, ","tha-ap148:4.2":"ekaggo susamahito; ","tha-ap148:4.3":"Dharemi antimam deham, ","tha-ap148:4.4":"sammasambuddhasasane. ","tha-ap148:5.1":"Ito kappasate asim, ","tha-ap148:5.2":"paripunne anunake; ","tha-ap148:5.3":"Raja sabbaghano nama, ","tha-ap148:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap148:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap148:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap148:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap148:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma anulepadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap148:8.1":"Anulepadayakattherassapadanam chattham. "}